==Russian==
[[Category:Russian nouns]]
===Etymology===
Possibly from [[волк]] (''[[wolf]]'') plus '''кудло''' (obsolete for ''[[hair]]'') or '''длак''' ([[Slavonic]] for ''hair''); or from [[Greek]] [[βρυκόλακας]]. Similar Slavonic words: [[vukodlak]] (Serbian),  [[vlkodlak]] (Czech), [[wilkołak]] (Polish).

